Manage challenge packs

Usage:
  agentclash challenge-pack [command]

Aliases:
  challenge-pack, cp

Available Commands:
  check       Sanity-check a challenge pack YAML bundle (alias for validate)
  list        List challenge packs
  new         Scaffold a new challenge pack YAML starter
  publish     Publish a challenge pack YAML bundle
  validate    Validate a challenge pack YAML bundle

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for challenge-pack

Global Flags:
      --api-url string     API base URL (overrides config)
      --json               Output in JSON format
      --no-color           Disable color output
      --non-interactive    Disable interactive prompts (also honored: CI=true, AGENTCLASH_NON_INTERACTIVE=1, --json, no TTY)
  -o, --output string      Output format: table, json, yaml
  -q, --quiet              Suppress non-essential output
  -v, --verbose            Enable debug output on stderr
  -w, --workspace string   Workspace ID (overrides config)
      --yes                Skip confirmation prompts

Use "agentclash challenge-pack [command] --help" for more information about a command.
